{"word":"G3951 - παροτρύνω - parotrýnō - par-ot-roo'-no - Stir up","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παροτρύνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">parotrýnō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-ot-roo'-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Stir up</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - துரத்திவிடு"},{"paragraph":"to incite, to stir up"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <b>&#x03BF;&#x0313;&#x03C4;&#x03C1;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03C9;</b>  <b>otruno&#x0304;</b> (to <i>spur</i>); to <i>urge along</i>, that is, <i>stimulate</i> (to hostility): - stir up.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}